tags: i still can't believe i actually get to see you
summary: It’s officially ONE MONTH. A month until I see the woman I wholeheartedly love for the very first time. A month until I dance...
body:
It’s officially ONE MONTH.

A month until I see the woman I wholeheartedly love for the very first time.

A month until I dance like nobody’s watching and sing my heart out. 

A month until I get to watch the strongest, kindest most incredible woman I have ever had the pleasure to get to know and look up to.

A month until I conquer my fear of flying (2200 miles) on my own and it’s all for you.

I love you Taylor, more than you’ll ever know and I’m so excited to finally see you perform and doing better than you ever were.

See you in London!

London Night 1 - Section C3, Row M, Seat 12

London Night 2 - Section BK A5, Row B, Seat 13

body:
You ask me why I love @taylorswift? Good, now I tell you.

I have a shitty day today.

I open Instagram and see Tay talking to her cats.

I see Meredith purring and Olivia be so private.

I smile. I smile more.

Shitty day is over.

Taylor Swift doesn’t know, but she’s always there for me when I need it. Like a superhero.
